CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Creative Medical Technology Holdings Inc is a biotechnology holding company focused on regenerative medicine. It is formed for the purpose of creating and licensing intellectual property in the area of amniotic fluid-derived stem cells for therapeutic applications. Its core activity is stem cell research and the development of applications for use to treat male and female sexual dysfunction, infertility, miscarriages, and related issues.
